---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
const siteUrl = "https://theganjaclub.co.uk";
---

<Base
  title="About The Ganja Club — Editorial Policy & Medical Disclaimer"
  description="The Ganja Club is a UK medical cannabis publication. Read our editorial policy, medical disclaimer, affiliate disclosure, and how we operate."
  canonicalUrl={`${siteUrl}/about`}
>
  <Nav />

  <main class="about-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <p class="kicker">ABOUT US</p>
      <h1>The Ganja Club is a UK medical cannabis publication</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        We publish patient education, clinic comparisons, strain guides, and
        news — because most UK patients still discover cannabis is legal
        through a stranger online, not their doctor.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>
        Medical cannabis has been legal in the UK since November 2018, but
        awareness is low, information is fragmented, and the pathway from
        "curious" to "consultation booked" is confusing. We exist to close
        that gap.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our site combines three things most UK cannabis resources do not:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Editorial journalism</strong> — cited, fact-checked articles written for patients, not clinicians</li>
        <li><strong>Practical tools</strong> — an eligibility checker, clinic finder, and strain explorer that answer the questions patients actually have</li>
        <li><strong>Transparent funding</strong> — we earn through affiliate partnerships with clinics and product brands, always disclosed, never hidden</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Editorial policy</h2>
      <p>
        Our articles are written and reviewed by the editorial team. We cite
        primary sources — legislation, clinical guidance, peer-reviewed
        research — wherever possible. When we link to a clinic or product,
        the link is either editorial (we are citing a source) or commercial
        (we may earn a referral fee). Commercial links are always clearly
        marked.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>No brand pays for placement.</strong> Recommendations in our
        guides and comparisons are based on published data (fees, Trustpilot
        ratings, service models) and patient feedback. A clinic appearing
        first does not mean they paid to be there.
      </p>
      <p>
        Affiliate partnerships never influence what we cover, how we rank,
        or what we recommend. If we publish sponsored content, it will be
        explicitly labelled as such.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Medical disclaimer</h2>
      <div class="disclaimer-box">
        <p><strong>The Ganja Club does not provide medical advice.</strong></p>
        <p>
          All content on this site is for informational and educational
          purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical
          advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of a
          qualified healthcare provider with any questions you may have
          regarding a medical condition.
        </p>
        <p>
          Eligibility for medical cannabis in the UK is always an individual
          clinical decision made by a GMC-registered specialist after
          reviewing your full medical history. Our eligibility checker
          describes how the system works in general terms — it does not
          assess you or guarantee any outcome.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you are experiencing a mental health crisis or thoughts of
          self-harm, contact your GP, NHS 111, or the Samaritans on
          <strong>116 123</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        The Ganja Club participates in affiliate programmes, including the
        Awin network. When you click a link to a clinic or product and make
        a booking or purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional
        cost to you.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our affiliate partners include UK cannabis clinics, vaporiser
        brands, and wellness companies. Every affiliate link is marked with
        a disclosure statement on the page where it appears. You can read
        our full partner list and commissioning model on the
        <a href="/affiliates">affiliates page</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Who runs The Ganja Club</h2>
      <p>
        The Ganja Club is published by AP Collective Ltd, a company
        registered in England and Wales (company number 17047232). The
        editorial team is based in Bradford, UK.
      </p>
      <p>
        We are a small, independent team. The site is built and maintained
        in-house — no agency, no investor, no parent media group. Every
        article, tool, and guide is produced by us.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Contact:</strong>
        <a href="mailto:contact@apcollective.ltd">contact@apcollective.ltd</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Patient stories</h2>
      <p>
        We publish anonymised experiences from UK medical cannabis patients.
        These are real people who have navigated the system — their words,
        their experiences.
      </p>
      <blockquote>
        <p>"I had tried three different medications for my chronic pain over five
        years. My GP never mentioned cannabis was an option. I found out through
        a friend, booked a consultation, and was prescribed within two weeks.
        The biggest barrier was simply not knowing."</p>
        <cite>— Chronic pain patient, Manchester</cite>
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote>
        <p>"The eligibility checker on this site was the thing that made me book.
        I had been reading about medical cannabis for months but kept putting it
        off because I was not sure I would qualify. Four questions later I had
        my answer."</p>
        <cite>— Anxiety patient, London</cite>
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote>
        <p>"I was spending £200 a month on a private prescription and the clinic
        finder showed me two clinics I had never heard of that were half the
        price. That one page saved me over £1,000 this year."</p>
        <cite>— Chronic pain patient, Birmingham</cite>
      </blockquote>
      <p class="testimonial-note">
        Patient identities are anonymised. If you would like to share your
        experience, email <a href="mailto:contact@apcollective.ltd">contact@apcollective.ltd</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Corrections and updates</h2>
      <p>
        Medical cannabis policy, clinic fees, and product availability
        change frequently. We review and update our content regularly. Each
        article shows its publication date and, where applicable, a "last
        reviewed" date.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you spot an error or outdated information, please email us and we
        will correct it promptly.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
  .about-page { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 20px 80px; }
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .kicker { font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--green); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 600;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem); letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .lede { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .section { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .section h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .section p, .section li { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .section ul { padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .section a { color: var(--green-accent); text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px; }
  .disclaimer-box { background: var(--green-bg); border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px; margin: 16px 0; }
  .disclaimer-box p { font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  blockquote { border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); padding: 12px 20px; margin: 20px 0; background: var(--bg-card); border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0; }
  blockquote p { font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  cite { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-style: normal; }
  .testimonial-note { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 24px; }
</style>
